articles.title: 2025 Emmys predictions: Who will win, who will get snubbed
articles.description:
This year's Emmys promises to award plenty of worthy winners, with major wins for “Severance,” “Adolescence,” and “The Studio” all but assured.

summary: Major wins for Boston-produced shows like 'Severance' and 'The Studio' expected at the 2025 Emmys.
